I think what kind of apples here is important. They mellow out really well w the cheese (used feta), but you dont want the super sweet kind. I used a spiral apple cutter, it made the whole thing a piece o cake. This dish could be served to guests or just keep it in the family. Its really good,easy, and has a beautiful presentation. Served it w spinnach tortellini.